column1: // This file contains tests for which Dartagnan gives a different result than herd and thus we skip them in the CI
// For each of them there should be a proper explanation of why the results of both tools differ

// sb (po) is different for C11 than hardware models. In particular it is not a total order (due to C11 not guaranteeing the evaluation order of function parameters). See https://github.com/herd/herdtools7/issues/394 for a discussion
// The following contains AMO instructions which we currently do not support
// The following tests have spinloops which are not side-effect-free (due to the use of Exch) and thus we cannot verify their liveness
